RestFB 1.45.0

RestFB is a simple and flexible Facebook Graph API and Old REST API client.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.restfb
Contains types used to interact with the Facebook Graph API and the Legacy Facebook REST API.
com.restfb.batch
Support classes for RestFB's implementation of the Facebook Batch API.

Contains exceptions that RestFB may throw while attempting to communicate with the Facebook API endpoints.

RestFB is a simple and flexible Facebook Graph API and Old REST API client.

For detailed documentation and usage examples, please visit http://restfb.com.
